snippet.title: NALLI BIRYANI | Mutton Biryani Recipe Cooking in Village | Mutton Bone Marrow | Lamb Shanks Recipe
snippet.description:
Today in our village, We cook the Nalli biryani recipe using fresh lamb shanks. We use Seeraga samba rice to make this traditional biryani recipe. The special of this mutton recipe is while eating biryani, and we taste a lot of bone marrow with the meat.

We enjoy the biryani at the evening! The taste is delicious!

Episode 890 - 891: ‡¶®‡¶¨‡¶æ‡¶¨‡ßá‡¶∞ ‡¶Æ‡¶® ‡¶ñ‡¶æ‡¶∞‡¶æ‡¶™ ‡¶ï‡ßá‡¶®?
---------------------
The Nawab of Murshidabad is depressed, so he asks his montri to find a means to make him feel better. Gopal's wife creates a sweet treat called "Taler Bora" (sweet fritters). Will this sweet dish cheer up the Nawab?

About the show
-----------------------------
Gopal Bhar was a legendary court jester in medieval Bengal. He was in the court of Raja Krishnachandra, the famous king of Nadia in the 18th century AD. Such was the genius of Gopal that the King considered him a Navaratna of his court. His statue can still be seen in the palace of Raja Krishnachandra. Stories about his exploits are narrated in Bengal to this day and are immortalized in countless short stories. The stories are short, beautiful, humorous, and have a specific social message. Gopal Bhar is famous for stories of his wisdom, in which he outwits other fellow courtiers

Everyone is excited about renovation. Babita's brother is an architect, so he will be leading this project. Since Jethalal's dining table is broken, they sit down on the floor and have their dinner. There is a funny conversation which takes place between Gada family regarding the same. The next day, Saptarangi (Babita's brother) comes to Gokuldham society to take the measurements of all the houses. Stay tuned.

About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal‚Äôs Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. J & V United by Love |Jisma Vimal Wedding| #lovestory #weddingvideo #southindianwedding 

" " United by Love " is a documentary focused on our journey from starting out as friends and aspiring actors, to falling in love and making it big through YouTube and finally getting married to each other. We come from southern part of India and we feel lucky to have a successful relationship even though our families follow different religions. We personally thank "Enchanteur", a brand centered around romance & love, joining hands with us in celebrating our love and making it special . Riding towards more adventure in our life and career, we pause for a moment and share these precious moments with you all. 

Love always, 

J& V

snippet.description:

Episode 3808: Jethalal Ke Priya Mitra
--------------------------------------------------------
The client finally meets with Jetha and Taarak, but Champaklal comes and unintentionally reveals the truth. The client is unhappy because Jethalal has been lying so far. Champaklal assures the clients that his son is innocent and that he never intended to conceal the truth. Jetha admits that he tried to avoid the encounter due to his poor command of the English language. The clients agreed to the terms after being impressed by Jetha's regard for his father. Taarak informs Jetha that he has come to assist Anjali at her request. Jetha later arranges an intimate dining experience for Taarak and his wife as an acknowledgment.

Show Name ‚Äì Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah

snippet.title: Ehraam-e-Junoon Episode 17 Teaser - 27th June 2023 - HAR PAL GEO
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Ehraam-e-Junoon Episode 17 Teaser - 27th June 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

"Ehraam-e-Junoon" follows the story of a young and immensely beautiful girl named Shanzay, who is filled with pride and stubbornness due to her upper-class upbringing. Shanzay believes that money can buy everything, including happiness. 

Despite her high standards, Shanzay is yet to find a man who can impress her until she meets Shayan at an event. Shayan is a handsome young man from a middle-class family, who takes up a job as a pizza delivery boy to make ends meet. Shanzay who is immediately drawn to Shayan wants to provide him with a better lifestyle however, Shayan keeps his distance and refuses to accept any of Shanzay‚Äôs advances.

As the story unfolds, Shanzay and Shayan's paths cross again and again, and Shanzay begins to question her beliefs about love and money. Will Shayan be the one to break through Shanzay's walls of pride and stubbornness, or will she continue to chase after superficial things?

The drama serial "Ehraam-e-Junoon" promises to take viewers on a rollercoaster ride of emotions as it explores the themes of love, pride, and class differences.

Writer: Jahanzeb Qamar
Director: Syed Ramish Rizvi
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

Cast :
Imran Abbas as Shani
Neelam Muneer as Shanzay
Nimra Khan as Sajeela
Mahmood Aslam as Kamran

Aadi Khan as Jugnu
Birjees Farooqui as Farzana
Farah Nadeem as Shakeela
Kinza Bukhari as Shazia
Mirza Rizwan as Faiq

Ehraam-e-Junoon Episode 16 - [Eng Sub] - Neelam Muneer - Imran Abbas - Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream - 27th June 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Ehraam-e-Junoon Digitally Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream

"Ehraam-e-Junoon" follows the story of a young and immensely beautiful girl named Shanzay, who is filled with pride and stubbornness due to her upper-class upbringing. Shanzay believes that money can buy everything, including happiness. 

Despite her high standards, Shanzay is yet to find a man who can impress her until she meets Shayan at an event. Shayan is a handsome young man from a middle-class family, who takes up a job as a pizza delivery boy to make ends meet. Shanzay who is immediately drawn to Shayan wants to provide him with a better lifestyle however, Shayan keeps his distance and refuses to accept any of Shanzay‚Äôs advances.

As the story unfolds, Shanzay and Shayan's paths cross again and again, and Shanzay begins to question her beliefs about love and money. Will Shayan be the one to break through Shanzay's walls of pride and stubbornness, or will she continue to chase after superficial things?

The drama serial "Ehraam-e-Junoon" promises to take viewers on a rollercoaster ride of emotions as it explores the themes of love, pride, and class differences.

Director: Syed Ramish Rizvi

You have to come up with some healthy and tasty fasting recipes. I am trying to help you. I already have shown 2-3 upwas thalis. You can make combinations according to your taste and choice. Today we are making Ashadhi Ekadashi vishesh upwas thali. As everybody in the house fasts on this day and the fast lasts for 24 hours, just 1-2 upwas recipes are not enough. So I am showing you upwas thali. This thali contains upwas gulabjam, sabudana khichadi, varaicha bhat and amti, lal bhoplyachi bhaji, upwas vade and a ghavan. I am trying to make it healthier. You have to come up with some healthy and tasty fasting recipes. I am trying to help you. I already have shown 2-3 upwas thalis. You can make combinations according to your taste and choice. You can try this thali at home and drop a comment for me. Do not forget to like, share and subscribe.

Ingredients:
Sabudana Khichadi
‚Ä¢ 1 cup Sabudana
‚Ä¢ 1 cup Water
‚Ä¢ 1 tsp Ghee
‚Ä¢ 1 tsp Cumin seeds
‚Ä¢ 2~3 chopped Green chilies
‚Ä¢ 1 boiled and chopped Potato
‚Ä¢ A little Salt
‚Ä¢ 1/2 cup roasted Peanut powder
‚Ä¢ Salt to taste  
Upwas Gulabjam
‚Ä¢ 1 cup grated Khava / Khoya
‚Ä¢ 1/4 cup grated Paneer
‚Ä¢ 2 tsp Shingada flour
‚Ä¢ A pinch of Baking soda
‚Ä¢ 1 cup Sugar
‚Ä¢ 1/2 cup Water
‚Ä¢ 2 green Cardamom
‚Ä¢ Oil for frying
Upwasache Vade
‚Ä¢ 1/4 cup Sabudana
‚Ä¢ 1 cup Varai
‚Ä¢ 2 chopped Green chilies
‚Ä¢ 1/4‚Äù grated Ginger
‚Ä¢ 1 tsp Cumin seeds
‚Ä¢ 1/2 cup grated Pumpkin
‚Ä¢ 1/2 cup boiled and mashed Potato
‚Ä¢ Salt to taste
‚Ä¢ Chopped Green chili
‚Ä¢ Oil for frying
Varaicha Bhat
‚Ä¢ 1 tsp Ghee
‚Ä¢ 1/2 cup Varai
‚Ä¢ 1 1/2 cup hot Water
‚Ä¢ Salt to taste
Upwasachi Amti
‚Ä¢ 1 cup roasted Peanuts
‚Ä¢ 2 chopped Green chilies
‚Ä¢ Water as needed
‚Ä¢ 1 tsp Ghee
‚Ä¢ 1 tsp Cumin seeds
‚Ä¢ Cinnamon
‚Ä¢ 2 green Cardamom
‚Ä¢ 4~5 Black peppercorns
‚Ä¢ 1 Bay leaf
‚Ä¢ Water to adjust consistency
‚Ä¢ Salt to taste
‚Ä¢ 2 tbsp Tamarind-Gudh pulp
Upwasachi Bhaji
‚Ä¢ 1 tsp Ghee
‚Ä¢ 1/2 tsp Cumin seeds
‚Ä¢ 1/2 tsp Red chili powder
‚Ä¢ 250 g chopped Pumpkin
‚Ä¢ A little Water
‚Ä¢ Salt to taste
‚Ä¢ 2 tbsp grated fresh Coconut
Rajgira Ghavan
‚Ä¢ 1/2 cup Rajgira flour
‚Ä¢ Salt to taste
‚Ä¢ Water as needed
‚Ä¢ Oil / Ghee

Ehraam-e-Junoon Digitally Presented by Sandal Beauty Cream

"Ehraam-e-Junoon" follows the story of a young and immensely beautiful girl named Shanzay, who is filled with pride and stubbornness due to her upper-class upbringing. Shanzay believes that money can buy everything, including happiness. 

Despite her high standards, Shanzay is yet to find a man who can impress her until she meets Shayan at an event. Shayan is a handsome young man from a middle-class family, who takes up a job as a pizza delivery boy to make ends meet. Shanzay who is immediately drawn to Shayan wants to provide him with a better lifestyle however, Shayan keeps his distance and refuses to accept any of Shanzay‚Äôs advances.

As the story unfolds, Shanzay and Shayan's paths cross again and again, and Shanzay begins to question her beliefs about love and money. Will Shayan be the one to break through Shanzay's walls of pride and stubbornness, or will she continue to chase after superficial things?

The drama serial "Ehraam-e-Junoon" promises to take viewers on a rollercoaster ride of emotions as it explores the themes of love, pride, and class differences.

About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal‚Äôs Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Ep 3807 | 26 June 2023 | Teaser
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 3807: Hum Meeting Ke Liye Taiyyar Hain
--------------------------------------------------------
Bagha and Nattu Kaka have been fully prepared for the meeting with the clients, while Jetha has decided to remain mute due to his English language difficulties. When the client arrives, Nattu Kaka and Bagha greet him, but they are more interested in speaking with the proprietor of Gada Shop. Clients inform them that they only hold business meetings with the firm owner and not with any of the employees. Taarak enters the scene at this point, and Bagha addresses him as their supervisor to handle the situation. Finally, the clients agree on the meeting's agenda. Will Gada Electronics secure the deal, or will the meeting be a flop?

Show Name ‚Äì Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast ‚Äì  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3807, 26 June 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

           Yeh kahani hai ek sidhi sadhi, padhi likhi, pyaari si, Pratigya aur ameer, bigdel, badtameez Krishna ki. Isi taakat ke dum par zabardasti ki Krishna ne Pratigya se shaadi. 
           Pratigya ke sasural aur maayke mein hai zameen aur aasmaan ka faasla. Krishna ki haveli mein prem aur aadar ka hai akaal. Aise mein kya hoga Pratigya ka haal?            Yeh kahani hai ek sidhi sadhi, padhi likhi, pyaari si, Pratigya aur ameer, bigdel, badtameez Krishna ki. Pratigya ki parvarish hui ek sadharan par acche parivaar mein jaha padhai aur sanskaron ko diya gaya bohot mahatva. Wahi doosri taraf apne parivaar mein Krishna ne dekhi zulm aur paise ki taakat. Isi taakat ke dum par zabardasti ki Krishna ne Pratigya se shaadi. 
           Pratigya ke sasural aur maayke mein hai zameen aur aasmaan ka faasla. Krishna ki haveli mein prem aur aadar ka hai akaal. Aise mein kya hoga Pratigya ka haal? Waqt ke sath Pratigya- Krishna ne kiya hazaaron mushkilon ka saamna aur door hua dono ke beech ka faasla. Ek anchaha rishta ban gaya sacche pyaar ki misaal.

snippet.title: ‡¶≠‡ßá‡¶ú‡¶æ‡¶≤ ‡¶¶‡ßÅ‡¶ß | Gopal Bhar | Double Gopal | Full Episode
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to SONY AATH: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCBz9qbqujcjIavFmBJW2oZw?sub_confirmation=1

Click to watch all the episodes of Gopal Bhar:
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL5O3zv2ZcASjyj4E57V9IfXokmwsXcMUp

Episode 5 - 6: ‡¶≠‡ßá‡¶ú‡¶æ‡¶≤ ‡¶¶‡ßÅ‡¶ß
---------------------
Raja Krishnachandra has a new cow in his castle and instructs his attendants to offer him a glass of milk after dinner every night. Montri begins stealing the luscious creamy milk in order to avoid being detected. He begins to add water to it, thereby adulterating it. , how will Gopal catch the Montri this time? Keep an eye out!

About the show
-----------------------------
Gopal Bhar was a legendary court jester in medieval Bengal. He was in the court of Raja Krishnachandra, the famous king of Nadia in the 18th century AD. Such was the genius of Gopal that the King considered him a Navaratna of his court. His statue can still be seen in the palace of Raja Krishnachandra. Stories about his exploits are narrated in Bengal to this day and are immortalized in countless short stories. The stories are short, beautiful, humorous, and have a specific social message. Gopal Bhar is famous for stories of his wisdom, in which he outwits other fellow courtiers

Such was the genius of Gopal that the King considered him a Navaratna of his court. His statue can still be seen in the palace of Raja Krishnachandra. Stories about his exploits are narrated in Bengal to this day and are immortalized in countless short stories. The stories are short, beautiful, humorous, and have a specific social message. Gopal Bhar is famous for stories of his wisdom, in which he outwits other fellow courtiers

snippet.description:

Episode 39: Kaashvi Ke Andar Ka Maha Jadoo
-------------------------------------------------
Shashmaag abducts Baalveer and attempts to assassinate him in front of Maha Mahim Uttan. Baalveer retaliates, revealing his true identity. Maha Mahim is startled to learn that Baalveer has been faking his identity for quite some time. Maha Mahim attempts to seize Baalveer but fails because Baalveer flees. Benam, the strange tribal lady, warns Baalveer that his true identity has been uncovered. Under Aageel's control, Kaashvi attempts to harm Eva, but no one is aware of his actions. Kaashvi is experiencing strange feelings, so Veer suggests she see a therapist. Aageel poses as the therapist and pays a visit to Kaashvi.

Star Cast ‚Äì Dev Joshi, Aditi Sanwal, Ada Khan, Behzaad Khan, Aditya Ranvijay

*About* 
------------

           Yeh kahani hai ek sidhi sadhi, padhi likhi, pyaari si, Pratigya aur ameer, bigdel, badtameez Krishna ki. Pratigya ki parvarish hui ek sadharan par acche parivaar mein jaha padhai aur sanskaron ko diya gaya bohot mahatva. Wahi doosri taraf apne parivaar mein Krishna ne dekhi zulm aur paise ki taakat. Isi taakat ke dum par zabardasti ki Krishna ne Pratigya se shaadi. 
           Pratigya ke sasural aur maayke mein hai zameen aur aasmaan ka faasla. Krishna ki haveli mein prem aur aadar ka hai akaal. Aise mein kya hoga Pratigya ka haal? Waqt ke sath Pratigya- Krishna ne kiya hazaaron mushkilon ka saamna aur door hua dono ke beech ka faasla. Ek anchaha rishta ban gaya sacche pyaar ki misaal.

               Yeh kahani hai ek sanyukt parivaar mai rehnewale Modi khaandaan ki. Izzatdaar, ameer aur naamcheen hone ke bawajud, ghar ke sanskaar aur sanskriti hain inka saccha dhan. Iss ghar ko chalati hai choti bahu, Kokilaben jissey darte hain saare sadasya. Kokilaben ke bade bete, Ahem ki shaadi hojati hai Gopi se joh hai ek saaf dil ki siddhi saadhi, anpapdh ladki. Unke jethani ke bete, Jigar ki shaadi hojati hai Gopi ki behen, Raashi se joh hai bohot hi chaalaak aur nakhrel. 
              Raashi hamesha dikhati hai neecha Gopi ko aur karti hai uske liye mushkilen taiyaar. Par Gopi ka haath thama Kokilaben ne aur banaya ussey hoshiyaar. Iss saas-bahu ki jodi ne apne pyaar, dulaar aur balidaan se bandhe rakha hai Modi parivaar ko.

About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal‚Äôs Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in 'Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The residents of the housing society, help each other find solutions when they face common, real-life challenges and get involved in sticky situations.
